reviewText:
So dang funny you can watch it over and over. One of the best comedians here! Enjoy if you get it you will be pleasantly surprised!!
Cynthia Chidester

Suzanne Westenhoeffer, a lesbian comic from Columbus, OH, gives an amazing and hilarious performance here.  I've used it in my women's studies classes as an educational tool--she illustrates the ways in which stereotypes of lesbians and gays can be disrupted and examined.

Dr. Cynthia Mahaffey

Everyone and I mean everyone that watches this video loves it and immediately says that when she comes to town, they want to see her!  Fortunately, I went to see her out of town in Provincetown before she could make it to my town -- worth every penney of the trip!  I even got to talk with her and she is a very grounded blessed lady.

This tape is Suzanne's HBO comedy special.  It is  the only such video I've ever purchased.  It focuses largely on lesbian humor, but everyone I've watched it with, of any orientation, has laughed until they couldn't  breathe.  Suzanne is an absolutely brilliant comic.
